    {
      "item": "impl Display for Diagnostic",
      "reviewed": false,
      "intent": "Format a diagnostic for terminal output. display_with_root shows a repo-relative file path, selects an icon via the icon helper (✓/·/↕/⚠/✗ by severity×kind), formats as 'file: item: icon message', and appends a 'fix: …' line when a fix_hint is present.",
